---
import PublicLayout from '../../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Strategic plan"
  description="YAT College's strategic business goals and business objectives."
>
  <p class="breadcrumbs">
    <a href="/about/">About</a> · Strategic plan
  </p>

  <h1>Strategic plan</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    YAT College's direction for the next three years is shaped by four strategic
    goals and a set of business objectives that translate those goals into
    measurable outcomes. The plan summary below is the public version; staff
    and partners can access the detailed plan via the intranet.
  </p>

  <section class="plan-section">
    <h2>Strategic business goals</h2>
    <ul class="plan-list">
      <li>Deliver first-class education using modern technologies</li>
      <li>Provide service excellence exceeding user expectations</li>
      <li>Implement sustainable practices</li>
      <li>Expand the number of locations</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="plan-section">
    <h2>Business objectives</h2>
    <ul class="plan-list">
      <li>Offer students new ways of learning irrespective of location</li>
      <li>Expand throughout Australia</li>
      <li>Increase student numbers by 15% annually over the next 3 years</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>

<style>
  .breadcrumbs {
    font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .plan-section {
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
  }
  .plan-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-h3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .plan-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
  }
  .plan-list li {
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: var(--border-1);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }
  .plan-list li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
  }
</style>
